        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Bug fixes and dash tweaks]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Dash is faster and more frequent.
Fix enemy attack while dead.
<code>is_attacking</code> now available on enemies (except wolf)</p>
<p>Dash speed is 100000 with a 0.25s cooldown.
Enemy <code>is_attacking</code> property (except wolves that are just running and attacking at the same time).
Enemy used to kill you while dead but no longer.</p>]]></content>
