        <updated>2024-08-13T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[New game play mechanics]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>0.22.0 Release - Cloaking</p>
<p>This release introduces a new power up - the ring!</p>
<p>This ring allows a play to cloak. Once cloaked, a player is not visible to other players or enemies.</p>
<p>Attacking will decloak.</p>
<p>Shields cannot be raised when cloaked. Cloaking will take down your shield.</p>]]></content>
